<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00090</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT REQUIRING ACCIDENT AND LIFE INSURANCE COVERAGE FOR RAILWAY TRANSIT PASSENGERS</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : Insurance For Railway Passengers Act</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Aims to give focus to the security of the commuters who use the Philippine National Railways (PNR), the Metro Manila Transit (Metrostar/MRT3), Light Rail Transit (LRT) and the Megatren (LRT2) which is just apt and fitting for the government to give the public railway users the insurance that they deserve.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>CORTUNA, JULIETA R.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-06-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>NATURE : Economic</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Violago (015 2016-08-24)</td><td>2. Sy-Alvarado (032 2016-10-04)</td><tr><td>3. Panotes (046 2016-11-21)</td><td>4. Dalipe (000 2017-10-24)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON TRANSPORTATION ON 2016-07-26</td></tr></table>